org.eng.util

Class OnlineStats

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eng.util.OnlineStats
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public class OnlineStats
extends Object
implements Serializable, Cloneable
    Implements online calculation of mean and variance and also keeps track of min and max. Taken from http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Algorithms_for_calculating_variance#On-line_algorithm
    Author:
    dawood
    See Also:
